flowchart TD
    User[User starts translation] --> Route[POST /run-translation]
    Route --> Access[Check login and company access]
    Access --> Plan[Build sheet and column plan]
    Plan --> Job[Create background job]
    Job --> Worker[Translation thread]
    Worker --> SourceRows[Read DataEntry source columns]
    SourceRows --> Translator[Translation helper]
    Translator --> Update[Write translated DataEntry columns]
    Update --> Invalidate[Invalidate affected unmapped review rows]
    Invalidate --> Notify[Update job status and notifications]
    Notify --> Poll[UI polls job-status]
